title: Coast to Coast AM - Aug 04 2013 - ET Visitations & the Shift
description:
Date:	08-04-13
Host:	George Noory
Guests:	Daniel Davis, Jerome Corsi
News segment guests: Douglas Hagmann, Stephanie Quayle

Hour 1: First hour guest, Jerome Corsi talked about his new book, What Went Wrong: The Inside Story of the GOP Debacle of 2012.

Hours 2, 3 & 4: Author Daniel Davis discussed extraterrestrial visitation and contacts, prophecies, and a possible shift in consciousness or spirituality that is taking place.
